1. --
{ This chapter is intended to help users understand the basic setups of openings within the course. The informational variations show ideal piece configurations and pawn structures that you are likely to get.  Below is a list of openings I cover and will look to expand on moving forward.  1.e4 openings:  1. Latvian Gambit   2. Damiano Defense  3. Colorado Gambit  4. Elephant Gambit  5. Parham/Wayward Queen Attack  
  1.d4 openings:  6. Englund Gambit  7. Budapest Gambit  8. Marshall Defense  9. Baltic Defense  
  Other first moves  10. Grob's Opening  ----------------  I hope you enjoy the course!   Best,  InfiniteFlash }
*

