[White "2. 1.e4 openings"]
[Black "Latvian Gambit 1"]
[Result "*"]

1. e4 e5 2. Nf3 f5
{ The Latvian Gambit, a waste bin opening since it was popularized long ago. }
3. Nxe5
{ White grabs the central pawn. White has tried a million different moves vs the Latvian and this is the easiest one to play. }
3... Nc6 { Black can certainly play this. } 4. Nxc6
{ I'm very confident Qh5+ is completely winning here, but for simplicity, just take c6 & play d4. Don't think hard about it. }
4... dxc6 5. d4 fxe4 6. Qh5+ { This is obviously a disaster for Black. } *

