4... Qxe4+ 5. Be2
{ White scores an incredible 74% in this position. This is still very good for White, but the symmetrical structure probably means that it's not immediately losing for Black. }
5... d5 6. O-O Ne7 7. Re1
{ Black will find it difficult to move due to White's threats along the e-file. }
