5... Qd6
{ This is the mainline, trying to break the annoying pieces honing on c6. } 6.
d4 { Taking space. } 6... Nf6 { Developing and the most normal move. } 7. O-O
{ The most natural move. } 7... e6 8. b3
{ White will play Ba3 next and Black does not have a good reply. Black will be decimated on the dark squares after a trade of dark-squared bishops. }
*

