Qa3 8. Nd5 { This knight gallop leaves Black hard-pressed for a move. } 8...
Ba5 { Bxd2+ does not help things. } 9. Rb5
{ A neat hammer blow to lure away a defender from the c7 square. } 9... Bxd2+
10. Qxd2 Kd8 { Black can not defend c7 otherwise. } 11. Ng5
{ Black's position is comical: his king is stuck in the center and has minimal chances of survival. }
